{"tid":1386907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推出去】營救義士，成立「真相與和解委員會」","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:05:49.000Z","uid":266060,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6499bc43810a939f145ee814f5fca4d1949308","tid":1386907,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"44人被告暴動（最高可判監10年），我地可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n由於：<br />\n1. 示威者街頭抗爭，始終起源於政府引起廣泛不滿<br />\n2. 警隊是今次爭議的其中一方，與示威者有根本利益衝突，社會難以信任由他們負責檢控，只會覺得係清算而非檢控（persecution rather than prosecution）<br />\n3. 2016到2019證明，強硬檢控只會製造更多「暴動」、更多悲劇<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須成立：真相與和解委員會<br />\n</span></strong>由委員會查清衝突起因及所有人（包括政府、警方、示威者）的責任<br />\n並在幫助社會復和的大前提下<br />\n由委員會去建議應唔應該檢控、檢控什麼罪名<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">符合法治精神：</span></strong><br />\n1. Justice must be seen to be done<br />\n2. 法治之外，社會都要復和公義（Restorative Justice）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">凡有人性的，都應該站出來支持<br />\n</span></strong>200萬唔夠，就請300萬人都出嚟！"},{"pid":"68549bd7b3fcb6c56e99e051efc64e29acbe7463","tid":1386907,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f1f826fea85b67c40cc68f2a6468fbb80edfe5","tid":1386907,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe35e7b69cc239c3f22abdf684ea50a4c311071","tid":1386907,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a431aaf7ce1438d5f3866f36aa7f41c3414ad2","tid":1386907,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ae7fd7caf83dcefb115740aff047